displayProperties.name: Savathûn's Curse
displayProperties.description: Implemented at the wish of Savathûn with Riven's dying breath and reset with every death of Dûl Incaru.

displayProperties.name: Ascendant Challenge
displayProperties.description: The Awoken have long practiced the art of walking between worlds. Follow their paths and defeat the enemy.

displayProperties.name: Altars of Sorrow
displayProperties.description: The Hive call out to the darkness. Silence their screams and prevent their sacrifice.

displayProperties.name: Wandering Nightmares
displayProperties.description: Enemies of times past continue to haunt Luna. Extinguish their remnants.

displayProperties.name: Eclipsed Zone
displayProperties.description: Guardian actions on Clovis Bray's space platform have resulted in falling debris throughout Rathmore Chaos.

displayProperties.name: Lucent Executioners
displayProperties.description: Light-bearing Hive roam the world expressing their Light-given abilities on enemies of the Witch Queen. Track down these bounty hunters and remove the complication which they create.

displayProperties.name: Vex Incursion Zone
displayProperties.description: The Vex are targeting their efforts. Block their access attempts.

displayProperties.name: Terminal Overload
displayProperties.description: The Shadow Legion and the Vex are conducting an all-out assault on the city. Put an end to their destruction on Neptune.
